    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "INPUT SIGNALS"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Engine Speed."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "When starting, current is supplied to the clutch proportional to the cranking speed.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Accelerator ON/OFF."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "A micro switch on the accelerator pedal detects pedal movement and tells the ECU to energise the clutch. The switch also prevents stalling when the vehicle comes to a halt.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Throttle position."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Throttle movement is detected by the ECU, and clutch current is adjusted accordingly.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Brakes."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Brake system operation is monitored, and clutch current modified accordingly.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Selector lever position."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Switches located adjacent to the selector lever detect \"D\", \"Ds\" and \"R\" modes.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Vehicle speed."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "A vehicle speed sensor is located in the transmission casing, and senses output shaft speed.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. Coolant temperature."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Clutch current is adjusted to compensate for variations in engine temperature, ie if the engine is cold, the stalling point is raised.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. Air conditioning."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Aircon operation is sensed, and clutch current is adjusted to ensure that the engine stalling point is correct.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "9. ABS."
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Clutch current is switched off during ABS operation.",
      "style": "normal"
    }
  ],
